Access Dashboards on Record Page Tabs

Embed a dashboard on a record page tab when it’s an optional part of your users’ workflow.

When you embed a dashboard on a record page tab, users tap on the tab (1), and then tap to open the dashboard (2). When the dashboard opens (3), users can interact.

To learn more, see Build a Custom Record Page for Lightning Experience and the Salesforce Mobile App.
title: Embedding Dashboards on Record Page Tabs in Salesforce
